{"tid":713657,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"印度有美斯忠實球迷疑投河自盡","createTime":"2018-06-23T04:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T03:04:54.000Z","uid":31314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70ae62a93c80d3a724f5de3a1a495acf29799571","tid":713657,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"周四阿根廷以0:3大敗予克羅地亞，除了令阿根廷球迷心碎，遠在印度的一名美斯忠粉更在賽後留下遺書，目前行蹤未明。<br />\n<br />\n事發在印度喀拉拉邦的科特塔耶姆鎮，當地一名叫迪奴阿歷士、任職會計師的球迷，在賽前對同事說阿根廷今場必勝，而且他的偶像美斯會取得入球。可惜事與願違，賽後30歲的迪奴不知所蹤，只留下一張字條：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>世上已沒有什麼可看的了。我正步向死亡。我的死與人無尤。</strong></span>」 迪奴住在河邊，警方與消防員嘗試搜索，但水位太高、水流太急，令搜索困難。迪奴的父親說：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他在賽前曾對其他人說：假如阿根廷輸了，他會沒面目再見人。</strong></span>」 尼日利亞剛在D組分組賽擊敗冰島，間接令阿根廷重燃出線希望。"},{"pid":"c36dc2ce0dcc05ca9fb1d28e371667575c2541bf","tid":713657,"uid":2033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"Keyman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec18f1a6645bde67fbe873b9a55f97bf40868708","tid":713657,"uid":31314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"c36dc2ce0dcc05ca9fb1d28e371667575c2541bf","tid":713657,"uid":2033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"Keyman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"王騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dab37297baf1c5dcc8d8afcb082e7bb916b672","tid":713657,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:29:52.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"740e3c99476f633307e473537be167ffaaa01e65","tid":713657,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"如果出到線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\